Ubuntu 11.10
apt-get install libxerces-c-dev libapparmor-dev libcap-dev

安装gflags-1.6.0.zip
安装glogs-1.0.0.zip
安装lxc-0.7.5
    将lxc-0.7.5.patch拷贝到/usr/local/include/lxc中
    然后patch -p0 < lxc-0.7.5.patch (主要是为c++编译)


将third_part/hdfs中include和lib64相应拷贝到/usr/local/include/hdfs 和/usr/local/lib

mkdir build
cmake --CMAKE-INSTALL-PREFIX = .. ..
